Individual




Darryl Hartley-Leonard



Dr. Darryl Hartley-Leonard is Independent Trustee at LaSalle Hotel Properties. He  is on the Board of Directors at LaSalle Hotel Properties. Dr. Hartley-Leonard was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by PGI, Inc., Independent Non-Executive Director by Jones Lang LaSalle, Inc., Chairman, President, Chief Executive Officer & COO by Hyatt Hotels Corp., and Chairman by Hyatt Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Blackpool & The Flyde College.



